This is the last beta update (31-01-12)

Traps are now more easy Welcome to a Cbble Minigame! ================== This map is a course map in cbble theme. The map has been updated, and the things below has been affected: + Added sm_ar_enable 0 on spawnkill and 1 on map start + Added more sounds and soundscapes + Added goldfishes to some water places + Added more details + Added better optimization + Added changes to end + Added new present to end + Added decals on walls + Added effects and more details + Added displacements + Added and changed secrets + Removed Junk Information: ============ EVEN MORE OPTIMIZED. FPS ARROUND 230-320 Traps ================== This map contains 12 traps and 4 secrets Last Word ================== Have fun and please report if bugs or changes needed. Thank you for downloading.
